{"tid":1549724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不宜成立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T12:21:03.000Z","uid":307092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca8da5ef9667b0673b4ef594a597b3343df3d5c","tid":1549724,"uid":307092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"...喎<br />\n<br />\n吓<br />\n咁幾時先係宜<br />\n咩叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔知相關人士肯唔肯接受調查</span></span><br />\n咩叫<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知邊啲先係相關人士</span></span><br />\n吓<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">你查案之前乜嘢都唔知架啦<br />\n你會唔會話：<br />\n「唔知相關人士肯唔肯接受調查」<br />\n「唔知邊啲先係相關人士」<br />\n就唔去查案？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n成日都話<span style=\"color: red;\">未清楚</span>整件事既來龍去脈<br />\n依家<span style=\"color: gold;\">市民都幫你查埋啦</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">新聞都報道埋</span>啦(不包括染紅新聞)<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">比夠100%還原度你班所謂警察所謂證監會</span><br />\n都仲話要調查<br />\nFine 調囉 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但幾個月前既事 至依家屎都調唔出啲乜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁你班人又有咩用呢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家叫你成立個獨立調查委員會<br />\n林鄭一句話警察好抗拒<br />\n就可以唔成立<br />\n<br />\n喂<br />\n最少200萬人都對你(林鄭)好抗拒喎<br />\n咁你可唔可以落台？<br />\n<br />\n我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔會多謝你</span>動議撤回送中條例架<br />\n本身唔應該存在既野點解我要多謝你拎翻走？<br />\n而且<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">太<br />\n遲<br />\n了</span></strong><br />\n。"},{"pid":"8dbd3fc49d40eb2e649510599b373343c50e3782","tid":1549724,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"223aa6f623119e06c3ae7ff302558fb7e3328fed","tid":1549724,"uid":202876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食屎啦林奠"}]}